{"id":"house-of-god","term":"House Of God","source":"International Standard Bible Encyclopaedia (James Orr ed., 1915)","html":"<p>In <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 28:17\">Ge 28:17</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 28:22\">22</a> = BETHEL (which see). In Jgs, 1 and 2 Chronicles, Ezr, Neh, Ps, etc. (beth ha-'elohim), a designation of the sanctuary = \"house of Yahweh\" (of the tabernacle, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Judges 18:31\">Jud 18:31</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Revelation 19:18\">20:18</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Revelation 20:5\">26</a> the King James Version; of the temple, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 9:11\">1Ch 9:11</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 24:5\">24:5</a> the King James Version; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 5:14\">2Ch 5:14</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 42:4\">Ps 42:4</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 2:3\">Isa 2:3</a>, etc.; of the 2nd temple, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 5:8\">Ezr 5:8</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 5:15\">15</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 6:10\">Ne 6:10</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 13:11\">13:11</a>; compare <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Matthew 12:4\">Mt 12:4</a>). Spiritually, in the New Testament, the \"house of God\" (oikos theou) is the church or community of believers (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Timothy 3:15\">1Ti 3:15</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Hebrews 10:21\">Heb 10:21</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Peter 4:17\">1Pe 4:17</a>; compare <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Corinthians 3:9\">1Co 3:9</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Corinthians 3:16\">16</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Corinthians 3:17\">17</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Peter 2:5\">1Pe 2:5</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 28:17","Genesis 28:22","Judges 18:31","Revelation 19:18","Revelation 20:5","1 Chronicles 9:11","1 Chronicles 24:5","2 Chronicles 5:14","Psalms 42:4","Isaiah 2:3","Ezra 5:8","Ezra 5:15","Nehemiah 6:10","Nehemiah 13:11","Matthew 12:4","1 Timothy 3:15","Hebrews 10:21","1 Peter 4:17","1 Corinthians 3:9","1 Corinthians 3:16","1 Corinthians 3:17","1 Peter 2:5"]}